channel.title: Help with commands! ;d
channel.description: HELP!! i got a problem with my server... i can't do ::pickup While i am Owner... Can Some1 help me? i also are new in RSPS, So... i dont know what base mines is o.O ( but it's luckscape source) Thanks For Watching Hope u Got The Answer!

item.title: Help with commands! ;d
item.dc:creator: @staypuff staypuff
item.description:
@staypuff wrote:

Look in your command file. On delta it’s client.java while on pi it’s commands.java

change the player rights to a setting that will alow you to use it. (for pi owner is usually player rights 3 while delta is 3/4)

if you are usingpi your command is probably ::item #### ##### not ::pickup #### #####
